pull.title: Fix .gitignore policy in build_msvc directory
pull.body:
This PR makes `git` to ignore only auto-generated `.vcxproj` files, i.e.:
https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/4c2578706c70148fc001f42a0918a2fb10252b43/build_msvc/msvc-autogen.py#L14-L25

Fix #17287

issue.title: Bitcoin PR tracking
issue.body: The main purpose of this issue is to keep track of Pull Requests on Bitcoin since version 0.19.1 identifying those which make a porting LitecoinZ.
